{
  "texts": [
    "Besides, ChatGPT can adapt to individual learning styles and provide contextually relevant assistance (Kooli, 2023; Wu & Yu, 2024; Zhang & Tur, 2024), which can be particularly effective in programming education, where timely and specific feedback is crucial for mastering coding skills (Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023b).",
    "Several studies have discussed about the potential benefits of using ChatGPT in programming education.",
    "One significant advantage is its 24/7 availability, enabling students to seek help at any time (Sun et al., 2024; Yilmaz & Yilmaz, 2023a).",
    "This continuous access can lead to increased student engagement and persistence in learning.",
    "Furthermore, ChatGPT can address to diverse learning paces, providing personalized learning paths and adjusting to individual progress (Bravo & Cruz-Bohorquez, 2024; Sun et al., 2024)."
  ]
}